	(text "Import my common USB shits?\n\nI don't really need to fuck with 24V power supply, this is a tech demo.\n\nMake it viable as a pi hat? place SWD + SPI? or UART? to the XMC on the hat pins?\n\nI mean, why not? it's a fun mode of operation?  Copy off my hat boards, those are proven out now?\n\nYou Still need _somethign_ to be some demo IOs for ethercat.\nDrop a can txer down too.  (I mean, bonus points for making it have a jbtmarel 24v can connector?"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
